{"tid":60427,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"我喺沙漠度墜咗機，之後就遇到佢......","createTime":"2016-12-30T12:20:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T10:49:15.000Z","uid":10131,"like":51,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"360f6805fd948a73632c45c2e0f1f49ccabf0bdb","tid":60427,"uid":10131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T12:20:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我六歲嗰陣，有一次，見到幅好壯觀嘅畫，幅畫係喺本講原始森林嘅書入面，本書叫做《真實故事》。幅畫入面有條大蟒蛇想吞咗隻動物佢。幅畫係噉嘅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/wMpZ7p9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FwMpZ7p9.png&h=c5efb6f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本書上面話：「蟒蛇會就咁將佢地嘅獵物成隻吞落肚，之後就郁都郁唔到，要瞓六個月去消化隻獵物。」我諗咗森林歷險嘅嘢好耐，我就成功用枝顏色筆畫咗我第一幅畫。我嘅一號畫，佢係咁嘅：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/32eyqKy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F32eyqKy.png&h=9de6ff96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我拎住我幅傑作畀啲大人睇，再問佢地有冇畀幅畫嚇親。佢地答我：「吓？我點解要畀頂帽嚇親？」<br />\n我幅畫唔係一頂帽，係條蛇消化緊隻大笨象。我之後就畫埋條蛇裏面，等啲大人明我畫緊乜。佢地成日都想要人解釋嘅。我嘅二號畫係咁嘅：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/OLNmfgh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FOLNmfgh.png&h=7b44bfe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係啲大人叫我唔好理畫條蛇嘅入面定出面住，理下啲地理、歷史、代數同文法先。就係咁，喺我得六歲嗰陣，就放棄咗做一個偉大嘅畫家。我因為嗰兩幅畫衰咗而心淡。啲大人成日乜都唔明，要啲細路係咁解釋，係咁解釋，咁係一件好攰嘅事。"},{"pid":"1ae9b7fa052c1e25fcfbbe6750ed5f4d8396cdb2","tid":60427,"uid":22151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T12:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c57edb1dd90034821338649e82f742d5f2780441","tid":60427,"uid":59670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T12:27:27.000Z","msg":"小王子？"},{"pid":"fd47a45c8acf821d10fa51171e36bd8b95961d1f","tid":60427,"uid":10131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T12:33:14.000Z","msg":"我唯有揀過第二個職業，我揀咗做飛機師。我去咗呢個世界嘅一部份。不過講真，地理喺呢個時候都幾有用。我一眼就分到中國同亞利桑那。由其是喺夜晚認唔到路嗰陣，啲地理就更加有用。<br />\n<br />\n喺我嘅人生入面，遇過一堆人，遇過一堆事，仲喺啲大人入面經歷過好多，試過同佢地好熟，但係我都冇乜改過對佢地嘅睇法。<br />\n<br />\n每當我遇到一個睇落幾清醒嘅大人，就會用我幅仲 keep 住喺度嘅一號畫試下佢，咁我就可以知道佢明唔明白我嘅意思。不過佢地永遠都係答我：「幅畫係頂帽。」<br />\n<br />\n之後我都廢事提嗰啲咩野蟒蛇呀，咩野森林呀，咩野星星咁。我就會就返佢地嘅認知範圍，講下啲橋牌呀，哥爾夫球，政治，同埋領呔咁。佢就會好開心遇到個咁明白事理嘅人。"},{"pid":"6965cee2a574f131a816ba2f4a3a363cdd584479","tid":60427,"uid":10131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:20:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小王子？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自己譯ga <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02512f424c9ac86a6a60a4efaab566d9a539a98f","tid":60427,"uid":10131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:34:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2</span></span><br />\n<br />\n噉我就自己一個人生活，冇乜邊個係真正傾得埋，直到六年前墜機跌咗落撒哈拉沙漠。副偈入面有啲野壞咗。身邊又冇技工，又冇搭客同我一齊，我就的起心肝自己一個人修理晒啲咁難搞嘅野佢，仲要對我黎講係生死由關。我有嘅水都係啱啱好夠我飲八日咋。<br />\n<br />\n第一晚我就喺沙地上面瞓教，方圓千里都冇人住噉。仲慘過撐艇仔出到海中心返唔到轉頭。之後你可以想像下，我畀人嚇咗一跳，因為晨曦初現嘅時候，無啦啦有人細細聲咁嘈醒咗我。佢話：<br />\n「唔該&hellip;&hellip;畫隻綿羊畀我啦！」<br />\n「吓？」<br />\n「畫隻綿羊畀我&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n我好似畀雷劈咁彈咗起身。我捽咗幾下眼，望真啲，原來係個豆釘，佢仲好認真咁望住我。呢度就係佢張肖像，已經我畫得最好嗰幅黎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/atk2cmjl\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fatk2cmjl&h=2f86483e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁當然啦，幅畫就梗係樣衰過佢真人好多，不過都唔係我錯，因為我六歲嗰陣，我嘅畫家生涯已經完咗，最衰都係啲大人。搞到我嗰陣除咗條蛇嘅入面同出面之外，就乜都冇畫過。"},{"pid":"a2fee5946b3fda34090bc9957c518ea7916e2208","tid":60427,"uid":10131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:35:42.000Z","msg":"我碌大隻眼睇下自己係咪撞鬼。唔好唔記得，我係喺方圓千里都冇人住嘅地方架喎。個豆釘望落又唔似係盪失路，又唔驚，又唔似攰到想死咁，又唔似好肚餓，又唔似好口渴咁。即係話，佢完全唔似係一個喺方圓千里都冇人住嘅沙漠度盪失路嘅細路。<br />\n<br />\n當我醒勻之後，就問佢：<br />\n「咁其實&hellip;&hellip;你喺度搞緊乜？」<br />\n不過佢講多咗次同樣嘅野，仲要慢慢咁講，好似好重要咁。<br />\n「唔該&hellip;&hellip;畫隻綿羊畀我啦&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n當啲咁奇怪嘅事發生咗嘅時候，你唔會唔失去反抗嘅能力。喺方圓千里都冇人住嘅地方，就黎會死咁嘅環境之下，我好似好戇居咁，喺個袋度拎左張紙同枝筆出黎。之後我就諗返起自己一直喺度學緊地理、歷史、代數同文法。我就（寸寸地咁）同個豆釘講我唔鬼識畫畫。但係佢話：<br />\n「唔緊要，總之畫隻綿羊畀我。」<br />\n<br />\n因為我未畫過羊，我畫返之前畫過嗰兩幅畫入面嘅其中一幅畀佢。就係喺出面望條蛇嗰幅。不過我畀佢嘅答覆嚇到我呆咗：<br />\n「唔係呀！唔係呀！我唔係要條個肚入面有隻大笨象嘅蛇呀。蛇好危險之餘，大笨象又太嘥位喎。我住嗰度好細架咋。我係要一隻綿羊呀，畫隻綿羊畀我啦。」<br />\n<br />\n之後我就畫咗幅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1stn95mi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1stn95mi&h=2692f50b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢睇得好仔細，然後話：<br />\n「唔掂喎！隻綿羊冇神冇氣咁嘅？畫過幅啦。」<br />\n<br />\n之後我又畫咗幅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/opzkmi4d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fopzkmi4d&h=0cf01d93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢好寬容咁笑咗一下，<br />\n「你睇真啲，呢隻係山羊，唔係綿羊，有角嘅？」"},{"pid":"bca4b4ce906797c2ed9ecfe26cd5fbfe8e71de5d","tid":60427,"uid":10131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:37:09.000Z","msg":"我又再畫多幅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8n1akwyz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8n1akwyz&h=e3bc0ff8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同之前一樣，佢又話唔得。<br />\n「呢隻太老，我想要隻可以生存得耐啲嘅。」<br />\n<br />\n我已經忍無可忍，想快啲拆開副偈黎整。於是我就 hea 畫咗啲咁嘅野畀佢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/s8ztun91\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fs8ztun91&h=cd9df67c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我同佢講：<br />\n「呢度係個箱。你要隻綿羊就喺入面。」<br />\n<br />\n不過諗都諗唔到，佢見到幅畫之後塊臉好似識發光咁，佢話：<br />\n「我就係想要呢啲野！你估佢會唔會要食好多草呀拿？」<br />\n「做乜咁問？」<br />\n「因為我住嘅地方好細架&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n「一定夠草畀佢食嘅，我畀你隻綿羊好細隻架咋。」<br />\n佢用個頭痴住幅畫咁睇，<br />\n「都唔細隻架喎&hellip;&hellip;睇下！佢瞓咗呀&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n就係咁，我識咗小王子。"},{"pid":"8b386ea3435405a330beab68abb5b5fec28f60a5","tid":60427,"uid":10131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T16:46:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d1661ecf74a3876b3342bd356cea45f2eb6ee75","tid":60427,"uid":12386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T13:57:30.000Z","msg":"停左？"},{"pid":"81074fad5e5afe92745e2d4e03f6679eb5313694","tid":60427,"uid":10131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T08:53:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>停左？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似冇咩人睇"},{"pid":"62032debf01c1e8c136b78c25c0d778b08b8d3c6","tid":60427,"uid":19100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T09:03:46.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c56eb1c2672342fb20b03edd7a545ad61110db8","tid":60427,"uid":2736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T09:05:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"850015e3b7b64e2dcb25409c63fc5c34c0586e5c","tid":60427,"uid":3270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T09:56:56.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"4b4f172a7ce24c075f886e36a3054bd397686c54","tid":60427,"uid":16827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T10:07:42.000Z","msg":"Brother，好欣賞你翻譯既文筆，比原文易投入好多，而且圖文並茂，好有心機；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但點睇依個都係小王子既故事，你諗住山寨版咁係唔得Wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：等睇完樓主解釋後俾正評"},{"pid":"53b80e6f6999099a372e7c71afc9ac187b7bc84d","tid":60427,"uid":38888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T10:09:27.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"bf2b794655dfed537aa833b4ac7cd19d15865337","tid":60427,"uid":27359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T10:21:03.000Z","msg":"Good!!!"},{"pid":"c5a3eb150029134e47417fd9c6f5cddb7a19256f","tid":60427,"uid":3643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T11:11:36.000Z","msg":"繼續"},{"pid":"efcec2284a92d1663011a9860e310cddcc23e964","tid":60427,"uid":6589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T11:13:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ee85c07ebbbfacf55fe1a4520f480ea7ce1608","tid":60427,"uid":41112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T11:17:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4acb72951624f357a7ff3a1c5ed998292158235","tid":60427,"uid":13283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T11:39:09.000Z","msg":"想睇埋先"},{"pid":"56598e3b286c8c6ee84a45f739a69de14ee0e91f","tid":60427,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T11:46:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小王子？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自己譯ga <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n粵譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8675dc202166890543a9d41546cfc3c273499989","tid":60427,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T11:56:39.000Z","msg":"但係蛇嗰度轉做大蟒蛇(定第二個品種?)會唔會啱啲?<br />\n我唔肯定係咩品種，但我無記錯嘅話原文應該係拉丁文二名法品種名來，而唔係大包圍嘅general name (snake)"},{"pid":"cb8aec278ae062dd77cd4665acb10dc72da6f41e","tid":60427,"uid":10131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T12:39:51.000Z","msg":"原著： Le Petit Prince.  Antoine de Saint-Exup&eacute;ry (1943).<br />\n參考： The Little Prince, translated by Katherine Woods. <br />\n<br />\n小弟嘅語文底子唔係咁好，希望大家可以多多包涵。<br />\n我主要都會係意譯行先，唔會話一字一句都會完全一樣。<br />\n<br />\n同埋因爲呢個英文版同原著差少少，所以就算我唔係好識法文都要睇一睇。我譯嘅當中一定會有好多錯漏，希望大家指出同見諒。"},{"pid":"698a75bdf8401bb3a65372d0b5e387b2ee54ce22","tid":60427,"uid":9692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T12:42:34.000Z","msg":"我呢家只係見到佢係一頂帽 見唔到佢係蛇了"},{"pid":"53a2645eb943fcf4252978321d792284c671ec34","tid":60427,"uid":10131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T13:22:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我用咗好多時間先諗得明佢係喺邊度黎。小王子問咗我好多問題，不過我問嗰啲佢就扮聽唔到。有時候，由佢亂噏嘅嘢，就可以慢慢咁了解到佢多啲。佢發現咗我架飛機（因為太複雜所以我唔識畫）之後，佢就問我：<br />\n「呢嚿係咩嘢嚟？」<br />\n「唔係嚿咩嘢，係用嚟飛嘅，呢架係飛機，我架飛機。」<br />\n<br />\n我好得戚咁同佢講咗好多我喺天度飛嘅嘢畀佢聽。<br />\n之後佢就喺度大嗌：「咩話？原來你係喺天上面跌落嚟㗎！」<br />\n「嗯&hellip;&hellip;係啊&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n「吓？咁得意！」<br />\n小王子笑到 gap gap 聲，好似好開心咁，但係我就好嬲。我發生咗啲咁不幸嘅事，我希望佢可以認真啲對待。佢繼續講：<br />\n「咁，你即係喺天空上面嚟㗎啦！你喺邊個星球度嚟㗎？」<br />\n<br />\n我見佢嘅出現咁奇怪，於是我就問佢：<br />\n「你喺第二個星球度嚟嘅？」<br />\n但係，佢冇答到我。佢擰轉頭去望我架飛機。<br />\n「原來係咁，即係你唔係由咁遠水路過嚟嘅&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n之後，佢就好似喺度唔知諗緊咩咁，一路就係咁過咗好耐。突然之間，佢喺個袋度拎咗我畫畀佢嗰幅羊嘅畫出嚟。佢望實呢件寶物，好似畀佢吸咗入去咁。"},{"pid":"c9a9a349a116f71a9a359d00f95d7f962106fa69","tid":60427,"uid":10131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T13:22:59.000Z","msg":"你可以想像到，佢咁樣講會令我想知道更多關於「第二個星球」嘅嘢。我就 chok 吓佢：<br />\n「小朋友呀，咁呢，你即係喺邊度嚟㗎？你屋企喺邊㗎？你&hellip;會帶我隻綿羊去邊㗎？」<br />\n<br />\n佢諗咗一陣之後答我：<br />\n「你畀我個箱都幾有用，夜晚可以畀佢當屋用。」<br />\n「梗係！同埋呢，如果你乖嘅話，我畀條繩你添吖！咁你日頭就可以綁住佢嘞。仲有，畀埋條木樁你。」<br />\n「唔係掛，綁住佢？咁嘅嘢你都做得出！」<br />\n「但係你唔綁住佢嘅話，佢會唔知走咗去邊㗎喎&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n條友仔又試笑到 gap gap 聲咁。<br />\n<br />\n「但係，佢去得邊喎！」<br />\n「邊度都會，總之有路就會行&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n小王子之後好嚴肅咁同我講：<br />\n「其實，唔緊要呀，好細㗎咋我住嗰度。」<br />\n佢仲好似加添咗份傷感咁講：<br />\n「就算真係有路就行啊，都唔會行得去邊啦&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vsp7z0ca\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvsp7z0ca&h=91ce285f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9d3021cf4260a783929fd85858111012726bc84","tid":60427,"uid":10133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T15:26:10.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aca1c7980c7026d3f26a5c60d2781dc5c81288c","tid":60427,"uid":22967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T17:32:02.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"6a5e267d5f672c43de0a31cd5e7160a0249e6c3e","tid":60427,"uid":42083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-03T04:03:27.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"febb79e485875d0d2abe9b68a6604363287b552f","tid":60427,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-03T04:15:14.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"364becdd10891f246be6a230573c76abb7b8be2a","tid":60427,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-08T16:29:13.000Z","msg":"文呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d389ceb113f6b9200682a2d8900834cb1782a0a9","tid":60427,"uid":48729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-08T16:49:11.000Z","msg":"好期待！<br />\n<br />\n我每次講粵文發展嘅talk，都會用小王子做例子。人口少到好似冰島話噉，都有自己嘅譯本，而人口過百倍嘅粵語，居然仲未有。好希望你嘅譯本可以出版。"},{"pid":"2eb68a73e2d979d9ed6d74cafb7225551ec5ab4c","tid":60427,"uid":20407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T01:34:24.000Z","msg":"正評<br />\n留名<br />\nF5"},{"pid":"8e2543033986460be6ad6bddf0a74b3b023d57ae","tid":60427,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-10T06:39:13.000Z","msg":"文呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24065d128c953c60bc55869839ef9d01cfe016ec","tid":60427,"uid":31859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-10T06:47:16.000Z","msg":"樓主幾好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54131db11490f5b03b054e4ae2792fecda971699","tid":60427,"uid":10131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-10T07:33:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我就係咁發現咗第二樣好重要嘅嘢：小王子住嗰個星球只係大過間屋少少！<br />\n<br />\n不過我就唔會覺得好驚訝。因爲我知道，除咗一啲比較大嘅星球，例如地球、木星、火星、金星呢啲會畀個名佢之外，仲有其他幾百個細小嘅星球，連用望遠鏡都好難睇得清楚。當有天文學家發現到個呢啲星球，佢會畀個冧吧佢做名。例如，個星球會叫做「325號小行星」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://wikilivres.ca/w/images/0/03/Telescope.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwikilivres.ca%2Fw%2Fimages%2F0%2F03%2FTelescope.jpg&h=5f42c3e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我有合理嘅理由相信，小王子住嘅星球就係 B612 號小行星。呢個小行星係喺 1909 年由一位土耳其天文學家用望遠鏡發現嘅，當時只係得一次觀測記錄。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://wikilivres.ca/w/images/3/3c/Astronome_turc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwikilivres.ca%2Fw%2Fimages%2F3%2F3c%2FAstronome_turc.jpg&h=fb4ec5bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢之後就去咗國際天文學聯會，將佢嘅發現展示畀人睇。不過，啲人因爲佢嘅衣着而唔信佢。啲大人就係咁㗎啦。<br />\n<br />\n好彩，因爲 B612 號小行星太過出名嘅關係，土耳其嘅獨裁者就用死亡嚟威脅佢哋，逼佢哋一定要着到好似歐洲人咁。個天文學家喺 1920 年再將佢嘅發現展示畀人睇。不過，今次佢就着得好光鮮。就係咁，今次全世界都同意佢喇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://wikilivres.ca/w/images/c/c3/Habille_a_l_Europeenne.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwikilivres.ca%2Fw%2Fimages%2Fc%2Fc3%2FHabille_a_l_Europeenne.jpg&h=a55c0274&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果我要同你講 B612 號小行星嘅嘢，我就會講一啲關於佢嘅數字。咁做係因爲啲大人。啲大人係好中意數字嘅。當你同佢哋講，關於你嘅新朋友嘅嘢嗰陣，佢哋永遠都唔會問啲重要嘢。佢哋唔會問：「佢把聲係點㗎？」「佢中意玩啲咩？」「佢有冇儲蝴蝶？」<br />\n<br />\n佢哋會問：「佢幾多歲？」「佢有幾多個兄弟？」「佢幾多磅？」「佢爸爸搵幾多錢一個月？」淨係咁，佢哋先會信你係識佢嘅。如果你同啲大人講：「我見到有間屋外牆係用玫瑰紅磚砌嘅，窗口放咗啲天竺葵喺度，屋頂仲有啲白鴿喺度&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n佢哋咁樣係想像唔到間屋其實係點。你要同佢哋講：「我見到間屋係值十萬法郎。」佢哋就會大嗌：「嘩！間屋好正喎！」<br />\n<br />\n同一個道理，如果你同佢哋講：「小王子存在嘅證據，就係佢好得人中意，佢笑過，同埋佢想要一隻綿羊。當一個人想要一隻綿羊，咁就證明佢係存在嘅。」佢哋都費事睬你，仲會當你係小朋友。但係如果你話：「佢來自嘅星球係 B612 號小行星。」咁佢哋先會信，同埋唔再追問落去。佢哋就係咁。唔可以對佢哋咁高要求。小朋友要多啲包容吓啲大人。"},{"pid":"fe313cba9b0772e858f240a39193f040c9703abe","tid":60427,"uid":33749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-10T07:45:39.000Z","msg":"惟有飲者留其名"},{"pid":"0a4421e324723a19be01cfed9d8929c85ca4d911","tid":60427,"uid":16922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-10T07:56:22.000Z","msg":"Keep going"},{"pid":"2a222719a7905dde7a56bc7185eb04b67b6a1415","tid":60427,"uid":10131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-10T12:18:38.000Z","msg":"不過，當然啦，清楚人生係點嘅我哋，就會不屑去用數字！唔係我就會好似童話故事咁寫呢個故仔。我會話：<br />\n「從前，有個小王子，佢住喺一個好細嘅星球，個星球淨係大過佢少少，佢想要個朋友&hellip;&hellip;」清楚人生係點嘅人，就可以得到更多資料。<br />\n<br />\n不過我又唔想睇我本書嘅人睇得咁求其。寫低呢啲回憶搞到我不知幾傷心。由我朋友帶走佢隻綿羊到而家已經六年喇。我要喺呢度講吓佢，係因爲我唔想忘記佢。將朋友忘記係一件好慘嘅事嚟，因爲唔係個個都有朋友。唔係嘅話，我就會變到好似啲大人咁，淨係對數字有興趣。<br />\n<br />\n所以我去買咗啲顏料同幾支鉛筆。喺我咁嘅年紀，係幾難重新去畫返畫，仲要講緊呢個人係除咗條大蟒蛇嘅入面同出面之外，就乜都冇畫過，嗰陣仲要得六歲！我之後當然就試吓去畫啲肖像，盡我能力畫到最真。但係我唔可以肯定我有成功到。有一幅都畫幾好，另一幅就畫得唔似。我成日都畫錯高度。呢張小王子太高，嗰張又太矮。我又唔係好知佢啲衫應該油咩色好。我就試吓呢樣，試吓嗰樣，有好嘅，都有唔好嘅。有啲重要嘅細節都畫得唔係幾好。但係應該要原諒我。我朋友咩都唔同我講清楚。佢可能以爲我同佢好似。但係，我其實唔識得望穿個盒入面去睇隻綿羊。我可能更加似大人。我已經變老喇。"},{"pid":"cd8460ee2be758f733335dc4756aa2a1572354db","tid":60427,"uid":72253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-10T15:18:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正皮"},{"pid":"5fe7de779f3264addc76bfdd853d974a8ea483ae","tid":60427,"uid":10131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-11T15:03:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">5</span></span><br />\n<br />\n每一日，我都會知道多啲關於佢嘅星球，佢點樣出發，同埋佢嘅旅程。關於佢嘅嘢我都知得好慢，佢都係無啦啦諗都就講咁。所以到咗第三日，我就係咁知道咗關於巴歐巴樹嘅問題。<br />\n<br />\n今次真係又要多謝隻綿羊，因爲小王子突然間問我：<br />\n「係真㗎可，係唔係呀，綿羊會食灌木㗎？」<br />\n「係啊，係真㗎。」<br />\n「啊！我好開心啊！」<br />\n<br />\n我唔明點解綿羊會食灌木呢樣嘢係咁重要。但係小王子再講：<br />\n「咁所以，佢哋都會食巴歐巴樹？」<br />\n<br />\n我就提小王子，巴歐巴樹唔係灌木嚟，而係成座教堂咁大嘅樹嚟。就算佢帶一班大笨象去，班大笨象都搞唔掂一棵巴歐巴樹。<br />\n<br />\n一班大笨象呢個諗法引到小王子喺度笑：<br />\n「咁要放一隻上另外一隻上面先得&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://wikilivres.ca/w/images/a/a7/Elephants.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwikilivres.ca%2Fw%2Fimages%2Fa%2Fa7%2FElephants.jpg&h=e9c23f58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過佢之後好醒咁講：<br />\n「啲巴歐巴樹，喺長大之前，係由細細棵開始嘅。」<br />\n「啱啊！但係，點解你想你嘅綿羊去食啲巴歐巴樹苗嘅？」<br />\n<br />\n佢答我：「好！就係咁！」好似講緊啲一定係真嘅事咁。即係我要自己，用我嘅智慧，諗掂呢個問題嘅答案。<br />\n<br />\n咁其實，喺小王子嘅星球上面，會好似其他星球咁，有好嘅植物，亦都有壞嘅植物。所以，咁即係會有好嘅種子同壞嘅種子。但係啲種子係好難搵嘅。佢哋匿埋喺泥土嘅深處度瞓覺，直至有一粒發完好夢瞓醒。佢之後伸個懶腰，怕怕醜醜咁，向太陽嘅方向伸出嫩芽。如果係蘿蔔或者係玫瑰嘅嫩芽，就由得佢想點生就點生。如果係壞嘅植物，一見到就要即刻掹咗佢。而家呢，喺小王子嘅星球上面，有一啲好恐怖嘅種子，就係巴歐巴樹嘅種子。星球上面嘅土壤就會畀佢哋用曬。巴歐巴樹嚟講，如果太遲掹走嘅話，就永遠都整佢哋唔走。佢會霸曬成個星球，佢啲根都會整穿個星球。個星球太細，而巴歐巴樹又太多嘅話，個星球就會爆開。"},{"pid":"9c021016a80543a18699ab9330f6f6d289dc24d0","tid":60427,"uid":10131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-13T08:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://wikilivres.ca/w/images/6/62/Toilette_de_la_planete.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwikilivres.ca%2Fw%2Fimages%2F6%2F62%2FToilette_de_la_planete.jpg&h=6aca00e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「呢個係紀律嘅問題。」小王子之後同我講。「當朝早清潔完自己之後，就應該好小心咁幫個星球清潔。要定期掹走啲巴歐巴樹嘅幼苗，仲要係喺認到佢唔係玫瑰之後。開頭佢哋嘅幼苗其實都幾難分。係好厭倦嘅工作嚟嘅，不過就好易做。」<br />\n<br />\n有一日，佢建議我要畫啲畫，等唔同嘅畫面可以進入我屋企啲小朋友嘅腦海入面。「如果佢哋有一日去旅行，」佢同我講，「會對佢哋幾有用。有時有啲嘢遲啲先做都冇咩問題。但係，巴歐巴樹呢樣嘢嚟講，遲啲先做就會好大鑊。我知道有個星球，住喺嗰度嗰個人好懶。佢冇理到三棵幼苗&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n根據小王子畀我嘅資料，我畫低咗嗰個星球。我唔係幾中意好似站喺道德高地上面講嘢咁。但係，冇咩人清楚巴歐巴樹有幾危險，呢個風險好大，後果可以好嚴重。只此一次，我破例咁講：「小朋友！小心啲巴歐巴樹！」咁講係爲咗警告我嘅朋友有危險，唔使好似我咁，長時間喺危險嘅邊緣，所以我畀心機畫咗呢幅畫。<br />\n<br />\n我得到嘅教訓都係值得嘅。你可能會問：「點解喺呢本書入面，其他嘅畫 都冇巴歐巴樹幅畫咁壯觀？答案好簡單：我已經盡咗力，但係其他畫真係畫得唔係幾好。當我畫巴歐巴樹嗰陣好緊急嘅思緒影響住我。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://wikilivres.ca/w/images/4/4d/Baobabs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwikilivres.ca%2Fw%2Fimages%2F4%2F4d%2FBaobabs.jpg&h=648e6f55&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d02ebb55a6352945002053e5190f2d604fe5d4f3","tid":60427,"uid":10131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-13T09:19:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">6</span></span><br />\n<br />\n啊！小王子，我逐少逐少咁，了解到，你呢種憂鬱嘅生活。喺一段好長嘅時間，你嘅娛樂就係觀賞日落。喺第四日嘅朝早，我就知道咗呢樣嘢。你同我講：<br />\n「我好中意睇日落㗎。我哋去睇日落吖&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n「但係要等陣&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n「等啲咩啊？」<br />\n「等太陽落山囉&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n你初頭好似好驚訝咁，之後你就喺度笑自己。又同我講：<br />\n「我成日以爲自己係喺屋企！」<br />\n<br />\n事實上，全世界都知道，美國係中午嘅時候，法國已經係黃昏。一分鐘內飛到去法國嘅話，都仲睇得切日落嘅。不過唔好意思，法國真係好遠。但係如果你喺一個好細嘅星球上面嘅話，只要拉一拉張凳就得。你想睇幾多次黃昏就睇幾多次。<br />\n<br />\n「有一日，我睇咗四十四次日落！」<br />\n過咗一陣，你再話：<br />\n「你都知㗎啦，當一個人好唔開心嗰陣，就會好中意睇日落。」<br />\n「睇咗四十四次日落嗰日，你係咪好唔開心？」<br />\n不過小王子冇答到我。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://wikilivres.ca/w/images/7/74/Coucher_de_soleil.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwikilivres.ca%2Fw%2Fimages%2F7%2F74%2FCoucher_de_soleil.jpg&h=f89474d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"809771fc1173961f9284718420f9649ae5036218","tid":60427,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-13T17:48:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a36508e09cb0a3d8bdf6786b66b169aa739fe3ac","tid":60427,"uid":45290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-13T18:20:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n全靠巴打一推我先可以睇到"},{"pid":"87c2b9419a05dcb64c273d115ea19630cc97b962","tid":60427,"uid":10131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-14T04:16:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝你成日都幫我推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54dfe12412acb2742808464aa5c1b995087b4d07","tid":60427,"uid":10216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-14T04:50:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0efc10009fce62dd9e6bbbef446d5fee86418ab0","tid":60427,"uid":54287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-14T07:33:58.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"f73c20d8da9a75ddd2dd7695ceaefbaa71607e16","tid":60427,"uid":10133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T04:09:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f6454d635afb72356db358d865735f160c6f345","tid":60427,"uid":59526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T04:32:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7981beaf5f2754cd78c44edf7b2718ab614fbe4","tid":60427,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T17:58:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝你成日都幫我推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n快啲出文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"265921d9105ed7075bec9694994990b4dfcff92e","tid":60427,"uid":10131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T12:21:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">7</span></span><br />\n<br />\n第五日，真係又要多謝隻綿羊，我又知道多咗更多小王子嘅祕密。佢好似已經沉思咗好耐之後，無啦啦好九唔搭八咁問我：<br />\n<br />\n「如果隻綿羊係食灌木嘅話，咁佢都會食花嘅？」<br />\n「綿羊會食曬佢見到嘅嘢。」<br />\n「連有勒嘅花都會食？」<br />\n「係，有勒嘅都會。」<br />\n「啲勒呢，係有咩用㗎？」<br />\n<br />\n呢樣嘢我唔知道。我好忙咁喺度嘗試擰開副偈入面一粒好緊嘅螺絲。我開始發現啲嘢壞得好嚴重，咁樣搞到我好擔心。而我最擔心嘅係已經冇乜飲用水。<br />\n<br />\n「啲勒係有咩用㗎？」<br />\n<br />\n小王子問咗嘅問題，佢係永遠都唔會放棄。粒螺絲搞到我唔係幾耐煩，我就是但答啲野：<br />\n「啲勒呢，其實冇用嘅，只係啲花想整估你架啫！」<br />\n「噢！」<br />\n<br />\n但係靜咗一靜之後，佢好大怨氣咁對住我話：<br />\n「我唔信你呀！啲花係好柔弱㗎。佢地好天真㗎。佢哋會令自己放心，佢哋會覺得佢哋嘅勒係嚇到人嘅&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n我冇應佢。同時我同自己講：「如果粒螺絲仲係轉唔到，我就用個鎚仔揼開佢。」小王子又再騷擾我諗嘢：<br />\n「而你，真係相信，啲花&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n「唔係！唔係！我咩都唔信！我冇經大腦講嘅啫。我有正經嘢做唔得閒！」<br />\n<br />\n佢呆咗咁望住我講：<br />\n「正經嘢！」<br />\n<br />\n佢望住我，我手揸住鎚仔，手指都係黑色嘅偈油，我攤係樣佢會覺得好核突嘅嘢度。<br />\n「你咁講嘢同啲大人有咩分別！」"},{"pid":"2cbbbe5b7deda6e621ca5fb08597170d5383a7ed","tid":60427,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T04:19:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba2e688a4c85c050a4abaffb0314e2f22064fe9f","tid":60427,"uid":1732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T04:24:31.000Z","msg":"譯得幾好 新讀者留名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd9d91a0dc2542e7d5d4204269615203399ad72c","tid":60427,"uid":68846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T04:53:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acffd1451a15cfbee65cafb9568e1cee1d27c35b","tid":60427,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T09:36:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\"