會有勒；自古以嚟，綿羊就係會食花。佢哋要搞咁多嘢，去整啲勒出嚟，而啲勒又冇用喎，唔通，去諗吓點解會咁就唔正經喇咩？綿羊同啲花之間嘅衝突，又唔重要咩？好高大塊面係紅色嘅先生，佢嘅加數，唔重要咩？唔正經咩？仲有，如果我，識得一朵花，係世界上獨一無二嘅花，得我個星球先有；之後，喺是但一個朝頭早，一隻細細隻嘅綿羊，一嘢就可以摧毀朵花，甚至意識唔到自己做咗，唔通咁都唔重要咩？吓！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://wikilivres.ca/w/images/3/35/Fleur_unique_au_monde.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwikilivres.ca%2Fw%2Fimages%2F3%2F35%2FFleur_unique_au_monde.gif&h=4a2ba064&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8cb819c064fde727c17901cfd121f12407bae170","tid":60427,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T16:45:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吓唔係一早有中文版咩?</blockquote><br />\n中你老母臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aae5370d5884259bc0d980a99180938411a290db","tid":60427,"uid":10131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:42:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>吓唔係一早有中文版咩?</blockquote><br />\n中你老母臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1bceb0ec9eec3bdc51f58e244343c474b7405de","tid":60427,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T00:03:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吓唔係一早有中文版咩?</blockquote><br />\n廣東話口語版就係有平時傳統書面語版無既生動有趣<br />\n可以吸引到平時唔睇書既巴打都去睇下依本好書 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}